    <item>
      <title>部长表示加拿大必须结束对廉价外国劳动力的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/canada-must-end-reliance-on-cheap-foreign-labor-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大移民部长正在采取措施遏制该国对临时外国劳工和国际学生的依赖，这引发了商业团体的反对，他们称没有足够的国内工人来维持部分经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/canada-must-end-reliance-on-cheap-foreign-labor-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:05:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
